Status Code's
------------------
GET(Retrive Data)
---------------------
200 - OK - Request success and contains request data 
204 - No Content - Request success but request data don't have content 

404 - Not Found - Resource does not exist 
401 - Unauthorized Access - Invalid key or access token (You are not logged in or didn’t provide the correct credentials.)
403 - Forbidon - Access not allowed.(dont have permission to access resource) - You are logged in, but you don’t have permission to access this resource.

401 = “You need to log in”
403 = “You are logged in, but not allowed”


POST(Create new record or resource)
-------------------------------------
201 - CREATED - Record or resource created successfully 
400 - BAD Request - Invalid Data - Missing Data

409 - Conflict - data/resource already exist 
401 - Unauthorized access - Not logged in 
403 - Forbiden - Logged in but dont have access


PUT (Update or Replace the entire resource)
--------------------------------------------
200 - OK - Resource successfully updated
204 - NO CONTENT - Resource successfully updated, no response body.
400 - BAD Request - Invalid or Missing Data

404 - NOT FOUND - Resource does noit exist


PATCH (Partial Update)
------------------------

200 - OK - Resource successfully updated
204 - NO CONTENT - Resource successfully updated, no response body.
400 - BAD Request - Invalid or Missing Data

404 - NOT FOUND - Resource does noit exist


DELETE (DELETE Record)
----------------------
201 - Created - Resource successfully updated
204 - NO CONTENT - Resource successfully updated, no response body.
400 - BAD Request - Invalid or Missing Data

404 - NOT FOUND - Resource does noit exist

401 - Unauthorized access - Not logged in 
403 - Forbiden - Logged in but dont have access


